headline: Danaher CEO to Comment on Financial Performance
summary: Danaher Corporation (NYSE: DHR) (the "Company") announced that its President and Chief Executive Officer, Rainer M. Blair, will comment tomorrow on the Company's fourth quarter 2025 performance in a presentation at the J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference at 11:15 a.m. PT.
